      <sec id="SEC2-2-4">
        <title>Basecalling and chastity</title>
        <p>Having corrected for spectral crosstalk, phasing and prephasing effects, we call barcode bases by selecting the nucleotide of the highest intensity for each cycle. We measure our base calling confidence by computing a chastity score (<xref rid="B33" ref-type="bibr">33</xref>)</p>
